10. How to use the application
Just open exe file in  aurora_catcher\aurora catchern application\dist\AuroraCatcher, upload allowed type of file in allowe resolution and click the button "Detect aurora".
The verdict will appear in the separate window. You can save it by clicking on "Save as txt" button.

11. Limitations
However the main purpose of the application is to say whether the aurora is present in the picture or not, it is expected, that pictures which are uploaded will
contain evening, night and twilight scenes with sky. Also models have been trained on such types of images. Uploading other scenes, like daylight landscapes, room scenes
or makro scenes etc. can lead into unreliable results. 

